content: RT @jsolomonreportsWhen Iranian hackers tried to send Trump dirt to Joe Biden, they also sent a powerful message to voters: the world’s most notorious state sponsor of terrorism (Khobar Towers to Oct. 7) prefers the Biden-Harris-Democrat policy of appeasement over Trump. https://justthenews.com/government/security/intel-community-iran-hackers-tried-pass-hacked-trump-campaign-information-biden

Iranian hackers tried to pass stolen Trump campaign information to Biden campaign: intel community
The intelligence agencies claimed the new findings are the latest in Iran's efforts to "stoke discord and undermine confidence in our electoral process." They also warned that Russia, and China, are also increasing their efforts to "exacerbate" division in the United States.
